// @test regression/INV014-const-arg-valid
// @description The const-arg check (INV014) must NOT flag genuinely-const arguments. timestamp(constString) resolves to the const-int overload; color.new(const, const) const-folds to const color; const arithmetic stays const. All three are accepted by pine-lint --tv. Guards the overload-resolution / const-fold leniency against future over-flagging.
// @expects parse: success
// @expects no-errors
//@version=6
indicator("INV014 valid const forms")
a = input.time(timestamp("20 Jul 2021 00:00 +0300"))
c = input.color(color.new(color.red, 50))
n = input.int(60 * 60)
plot(a + n, color = c)
